Fiston said he produced the new song with the backing of Nairobi-based Ketebul All Stars Band.Since 2015, Fiston has been visiting Kenya regularly for music production. Visiting UK-based Congolese musician Fiston Lusambo recently released a new video dedicated to Kenyan fans titled Jirekebishe Ogolla.
Fiston has in the last few years has been incorporating Kenyan and Congolese musicians in his recordings.
With the Covid-19 global pandemic having restricted live performances, Fiston, who has been in Kenya since December last year, is elated with the new production.



